metadata.name: Mountains are calling
metadata.description:
Mountains are calling!.. 
feel the peace and listen to the sound of nature. it's your essence  
portrait of those who answered this call.


- who collects the MOST will WIN a 1/1 AIRDROP from TNNUS collection.

- 2nd person who collects the MOST will WIN a blind mint from Hagia x TylersJourney Rafflegraphy.

- %10 of the income will be used to buy artworks

- claim ends in 09 December 2022

Happy Collecting
